# Backend Testing Rules (Extension)

## 1. Stub Rules
- Stubs must implement domain or application interfaces
- Must be deterministic
- Must contain no business logic

## 2. Stub Placement
- Stubs belong in Infrastructure layer (test implementations only)

## 3. Naming Convention
- InMemoryXRepository for persistence stubs
- FakeXService for service stubs

## 4. Backend Focus
- Emphasize domain and application layer correctness
- Prefer integration testing between layers when valuable